entry.summary: ...Strong Storm Moving to the Eastern Bering Sea and Chukchi Sea Wednesday Through Friday... A strong storm is developing in the Sea of Ohkotsk and will move to Chukotsk Peninsula Wednesday, and to Wrangel Island by Thursday morning. The storm will continue northeast into the Arctic Ocean on Friday.
